question: which business has the most number of checkins
query: SELECT T1.NAME FROM YELP.CHECKIN T2 JOIN YELP.BUSINESS T1 ON T2.BUSINESS_ID  =  T1.BUSINESS_ID GROUP BY T1.NAME ORDER BY SUM ( T2.COUNT ) DESC FETCH FIRST 1 ROWS ONLY
